{"id": "1368931918086934549", "channel_id": "1368890341490556948", "type": 19, "author_id": "1212339830835511347", "author_name": "muliupan", "author_bot": false, "content": "对哦角色启灵12+之后抽到会自动变成碎片，搞的不敢常驻12+，以前那个20+显然不合理，现在是找到新方案了是吧\n等我四分钟cd，有个很重要的问题想单开一段问", "timestamp": "2025-05-05T12:46:42.797000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-05-05T12:53:55.154000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["633215996508766229"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1368931679317524563", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1368890341490556948", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：1.5周年～战斗增强篇", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1368932304042459196", "channel_id": "1368890341490556948", "type": 19, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "主线的强度差异太大，故事也都有特定情况，所以共鸣不合适挪用。但我们在研究推出类似无尽模式，可能是一次性获取所有共鸣、成就、任务后就无需再挑战的关卡这种形式，但要达成这一点可能要游玩多次。", "timestamp": "2025-05-05T12:48:14.816000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-05-05T12:49:17.310000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["557599119401811978"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "❓", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}, {"emoji": "🤤", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1368929266879823893", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1368890341490556948", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：1.5周年～战斗增强篇", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1368932441842253846", "channel_id": "1368890341490556948", "type": 0, "author_id": "1317426621082370119", "author_name": "287405tjy_28066", "author_bot": false, "content": "灵核碎片太坑了，不说改成+12不再进池，至少也要给一下抽数吧，尤其是+12之后还吃了保底，亏死了，25个灵核碎片才能合成一个", "timestamp": "2025-05-05T12:48:47.670000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-05-05T12:50:06.246000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1368890341490556948", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：1.5周年～战斗增强篇", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1368932470212526201", "channel_id": "1368890341490556948", "type": 0, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "也许未来也能增加类似的不同模式。不过这个还很早，只是早期想法。", "timestamp": "2025-05-05T12:48:54.434000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1368890341490556948", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：1.5周年～战斗增强篇", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1368933096069660753", "channel_id": "1368890341490556948", "type": 19, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "是。", "timestamp": "2025-05-05T12:51:23.650000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1212339830835511347"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1368931918086934549", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1368890341490556948", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：1.5周年～战斗增强篇", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1368933874314379336", "channel_id": "1368890341490556948", "type": 19, "author_id": "1213364721328332840", "author_name": "akalanden", "author_bot": false, "content": "你也知道星辰篇主线难度大<:alone:1356053021318189307> 有没有考虑降低一些数值方面上的难度\n虽然看到在研究新玩法，但是我现在看到星辰篇的主线数值就完全没有动力去打即将推出的新主线和新剧情\n那我先躺墓里了", "timestamp": "2025-05-05T12:54:29.198000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-05-05T12:56:12.538000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["633215996508766229"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "✅", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}, {"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1368932304042459196", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1368890341490556948", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：1.5周年～战斗增强篇", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1368934073334108222", "channel_id": "1368890341490556948", "type": 19, "author_id": "456226577798135808", "author_name": "Deleted User", "author_bot": false, "content": "無盡模式 太好了 可以玩自己喜歡的陣容闖關了🥳", "timestamp": "2025-05-05T12:55:16.648000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["633215996508766229"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1368932304042459196", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1368890341490556948", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：1.5周年～战斗增强篇", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1368934093416304641", "channel_id": "1368890341490556948", "type": 19, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "暂时没有，不过我们会持续观察审视这一点。如果有必要的话会考虑的。", "timestamp": "2025-05-05T12:55:21.436000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1213364721328332840"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1368933874314379336", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1368890341490556948", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：1.5周年～战斗增强篇", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1368934492839870485", "channel_id": "1368890341490556948", "type": 0, "author_id": "1212339830835511347", "author_name": "muliupan", "author_bot": false, "content": "<@633215996508766229> 自选池以后都是这样只能选一次，然后角色和专武共占大保底的机制吗。这个池子的现在最多的别称是毒池，给萌新最多的推荐是别抽，这违背了开自选池的初衷吧。\n毕竟一直歪命轮的可能性是完全存在的。而且限定命轮60抽大保底，这个池90大保底，大保底歪命轮那一刻的赤石感是难以言表的", "timestamp": "2025-05-05T12:56:56.666000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-05-05T12:59:19.620000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["633215996508766229"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "✅", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1368890341490556948", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：1.5周年～战斗增强篇", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
