{"id": "1368935571703070814", "channel_id": "1368890341490556948", "type": 19, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "不行，正常是能打出按X，但是經常使用等價交換棄牌的情況下在某些情況會導致莫名bug，最終沒有半張卡進入腦缸空間", "timestamp": "2025-05-05T13:01:13.887000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1317426621082370119"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1368928796530577429", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1368890341490556948", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：1.5周年～战斗增强篇", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1368936446081237083", "channel_id": "1368890341490556948", "type": 19, "author_id": "855461987805822987", "author_name": "shchng.", "author_bot": false, "content": "可以優化一下船長的狂氣讓他可以自己選要把什麼牌丟掉嗎放到三啟也可以，隊伍通常是船長開狂上易傷開始輸出，把關鍵的輸出牌丟掉後就很難輸出，你也不能確保抽上來的牌會不會有輸出牌，他的狂氣效果就是給的很奇怪", "timestamp": "2025-05-05T13:04:42.355000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["633215996508766229"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 9}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1368934686851596318", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1368890341490556948", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：1.5周年～战斗增强篇", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1368938625286410342", "channel_id": "1368890341490556948", "type": 0, "author_id": "557599119401811978", "author_name": "heikwok", "author_bot": false, "content": "~~我覺得超限那3永觸改成3領航的話，實用度會高很多，放其他界域混編也能玩一下，即印即棄能吃到超限效果之類的~~\n~~不然吃200狂氣又要花算力印牌負擔太大，實際需要永觸的話找其他角色補也行~~\n~~不過觸腕有加強就算了~~", "timestamp": "2025-05-05T13:13:21.918000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-05-05T13:15:13.845000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1368890341490556948", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：1.5周年～战斗增强篇", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1368939184898834525", "channel_id": "1368890341490556948", "type": 19, "author_id": "944524613168279553", "author_name": "ena04564", "author_bot": false, "content": "保留哪幾張牌吧，如果一次丟很多就要一直點餒", "timestamp": "2025-05-05T13:15:35.340000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["855461987805822987"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1368936446081237083", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1368890341490556948", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：1.5周年～战斗增强篇", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1368943423289167932", "channel_id": "1368890341490556948", "type": 19, "author_id": "1212339830835511347", "author_name": "muliupan", "author_bot": false, "content": "那如果神图技能是把牌放置头顶蓄力，需要在打出n张牌充能才能生效，用来充能的手牌会消耗算力但不生效，但能触发余波。神图大招不靠狂气开靠消耗手牌就开且触发被烧的牌的余波呢。\n这样就能规避过牌丢key卡能利用领航，能烧垃圾，还能串联弃弃牌流", "timestamp": "2025-05-05T13:32:25.851000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-05-05T13:35:49.363000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["855461987805822987"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1368936446081237083", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1368890341490556948", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：1.5周年～战斗增强篇", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
